  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nIt would be helpful to have the option to see more output information when compiling contracts such as\r\n1. The number of contracts compiled - maybe grouped by core contracts and test\r\n2.  Solidity version - not sure how this would be displayed with different versions but some output would be nice\r\n3. Compile time - not crucial just interesting\r\n\r\nVerbosity could be added as a flag to build to control how much output to display.  \n\n### Additional context\n\nHardhat example\r\n![Screen Shot 2022-01-29 at 2 42 22 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8229664/151680156-1ada05f5-2ab8-4891-b3a3-bfc359dcf9e9.png)\r\n\r\nBrownie example\r\n![Screen Shot 2022-01-29 at 2 47 23 PM](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8229664/151680158-c3295fcd-e005-4f6d-906e-a9bf803e144b.png)\r\n",
